{"tid":815824,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"日本電影 啊～荒野  結局","createTime":"2018-09-12T10:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T05:10:33.000Z","uid":35166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe798632e83a4c052693c9883f8ea5c260865e4","tid":815824,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇過<br />\n巴打們可否解讀為何 建二 最後選擇 在台上由 新次    去結束佢生命？<br />\n<br />\n最後一幕建二 任由 新次 打足八十九拳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到心痛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己解讀<br />\n<br />\n第一部 講過拳擊係帶著仇恨去對抗敵人，直至自己最後成為冠軍<br />\n<br />\n所以最後一戰中，建二 對新次既（愛？）令佢不能去仇恨新次 ，所以自己放棄反抗 ，係想同佢一樣，令新次放下仇恨？可惜新次冇明白 建二既內心，繼續向建二揮拳，直到生命結束<br />\n<br />\n以上1999 <br />\n始終唔太明白建二為何去不反抗<br />\n<br />\n希望有看過的巴打們一齊討論"},{"pid":"644e2ed346d491db90a3c1cc09fa722f8d436188","tid":815824,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4d670027a6503a68d7fd4b0c0468f4ab1e51ce","tid":815824,"uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"主要係睇今野杏南兩點"},{"pid":"eb3511ef5a804d7a1d00ed1a10b1e7a09b40526c","tid":815824,"uid":208316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"Open Ending 建二未死 死個個係佢老豆 一定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a72ed6553bc978efd14f6303043ddd35bf200f6","tid":815824,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:01:54.000Z","msg":"有無seed,我要睇露點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5180abb82965c80aa17144b891b3820e9c89e7","tid":815824,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb3511ef5a804d7a1d00ed1a10b1e7a09b40526c","tid":815824,"uid":208316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018